<p><i><b>The Good Son</b></i> is a 1993 American <a href="/wiki/Psychological_thriller" title="Psychological thriller">psychological thriller</a> film directed by <a href="/wiki/Joseph_Ruben" title="Joseph Ruben">Joseph Ruben</a> and written by English novelist <a href="/wiki/Ian_McEwan" title="Ian McEwan">Ian McEwan</a>. The film stars <a href="/wiki/Elijah_Wood" title="Elijah Wood">Elijah Wood</a> and <a href="/wiki/Macaulay_Culkin" title="Macaulay Culkin">Macaulay Culkin</a>.</p>
<p></p>
